  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA43">
<l>tōḷiraṇ ṭeṭṭēḻu mūṉṟu muṭiyaṉaittun</l>
<l>tāḷiraṇṭum vīḻac caranturantāṉ – ṟāḷiraṇṭu</l>
<l>mārtoḻuvār pāta mavaitoḻuva taṉṟēyeṉ</l>
<l>cīrkeḻutōḷ ceyyuñ ciṟappu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will worship the two feet of him who shot the arrow so that the two</l>
<l>[times] eight arms, all the seven [and] three heads and both feet fell?</l>
<l>Worshipping those feet, isn’t it, is the honour</l>
<l>my excellent arms do [to them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
